Prerequistes to build:

-a C++ compiler (tested on gcc 3.3 and up)
-libboost (boost::shared_ptr)

-automake
OR
-CMake 2.4 <http://cmake.org>


Supported file format:
-Canon CR2: 20D, 350D, 5D
-Canon CRW: 300D
-Nikon NEF: D100, D70
-Olympus ORF: E-300
-DNG
-Sony ARW: A-100 (experimental/broken)



Support table:
--------------
T=tested (I have a sample)
Y=yes it is there (untested I don't have a sample but the format is know 
  to be similar)
N=no
B=known to be broken (needs to be fixed I have a sample but further work is
  needed)



                       ThNail

